name: podamShouldFillPojoWithEnums

testSteps.description: When I invoke the factory manufacturing for class uk.co.jemos.podam.test.dto.EnumsPojo
Then the pojo EnumsPojo ( ratePodamInternal = COOL    ratePodamExternal = EXTERNAL_SUPERCOOL     ) must be of the type class uk.co.jemos.podam.test.dto.EnumsPojo
Then the pojo EXTERNAL_SUPERCOOL must be of the type class uk.co.jemos.podam.test.enums.ExternalRatePodamEnum
Then the pojo COOL must be of the type class uk.co.jemos.podam.test.dto.EnumsPojo$RatePodamInternal
Then the Pojo should be null
